{
  "stem": "18281.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 150.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They, they declared-- they closed the university.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They, they, they had a general strike and used that time to ferry all their Jews to Sweden in little boats.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Only 500 of the 7,000 Danish Jews were arrested by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They went to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the Danes with Red Cross buses went to get them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They got them out of Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "With the exception of a few Jews that died in Theresienstadt, all the Danish Jews were being saved by their neighbors.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The homes and the houses of the Jews in Denmark were kept intact by their Danish neighbors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They went in there every week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they dusted the apartments.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When the Jews came back after the war, they had everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "All their belongings were intact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "If you couldn't be in Denmark, Belgium wasn't a bad place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The Belgians did their utmost to save a lot of children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They had orphanages.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They had-- in different cloisters, they had Jews hidden, just like my sister.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't think anybody knew, except the Mother Superior, that my sister was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And in the countryside, because of all the, the ill feeling against the Germans, the Belgians saved us and saved a lot of other people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, we want to save 5000 Jews and did it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we left-- we, we obtained the visa, an immigration visa, in, in the fall of 1951.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to undergo medical [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] inspections, you know, what they did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They tested our lungs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got x-rays taken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and we finally embarked from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
